# Implementation Plan - Bloco I Suprimento Migration Fixes

This plan aims to resolve the remaining TypeScript/linting errors and finalize the migration of the Administration (Suprimento) modules to the Ultimate V4.1 design system.

## Proposed Changes

### Lesson Components
Standardize the following files to match the [shared.tsx](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/shared.tsx) interfaces and correct the quiz data mapping.

#### [MODIFY] [AulaAdministracaoGeralSuprimento.tsx](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/administracao/AulaAdministracaoGeralSuprimento.tsx)
- Update [AulaTemplate](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/shared.tsx#2252-2532) props (remove `onUpdateProgress`, fix `modules`).
